dig|first=Dr Eviane|work=GNET|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105143728/https://gnet-research.org/2020/02/24/far-right-terrorism-is-global-but-coverage-is-not-hindu-nationalist-violence-in-india/|dead-url=no}}<br>{{Cite web|title=India’s ruling right-wing BJP suffers setback as as opposition wins polls in key States|url=https://peoplesdispatch.org/2018/12/12/indias-ruling-right-wing-bjp-suffers-setback-as-as-opposition-wins-polls-in-key-states/|access-date=2022-01-05|date=2018-12-12|work=Peoples Dispatch|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105184001/https://peoplesdispatch.org/2018/12/12/indias-ruling-right-wing-bjp-suffers-setback-as-as-opposition-wins-polls-in-key-states/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
